title: Looking For Old Match History
body: im looking for an old game I played anivia bot lane and went 14/7/9 but its older than the match history is in my client is there any way to find it again? I am specifically looking for the date that I played the game on. I know I played it sometime this month or last

replies.body: It looks like this account hasn't had too many matches played yet, so I'm assuming the match wasn't played on this account. If you aren't seeing it in your match history, you might be able to find it on a website like op.gg or lolking.net.

uuuuuuuh. i was on the beta tester for the new client and i actually started playing back when you re-released gangplank... sooooo why does it look like i don't have too many matches played? should i be concerned?
